HomeWiki:
Multi-threaded WPF app buillt with DotNetZip.

This app shows how to set up DotNetZip with WPF multi-threading it is also set up to password protect the archive using AES256 encryption.

This solution was written with C# and was built with Visual Studio 2013 Ultimate.
